# $5 = nppc
# $6 = nstep
# $7 = nrestart
# $8 = size
#
#######################################################################
# Create the input decks for 1 thread/rank i.e. MPI only case.

#---------------------------------------------------
#                $1    $2   $3  $4  $5  $6  $7   $8
#---------------------------------------------------
